item.title: CVE-2024-43942|2024-08-29T15:27:25.130Z -- wpsoul -- greenshift%20query%20and%20meta%20addon
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection') vulnerability in Wpsoul Greenshift Query and Meta Addon allows SQL Injection.This issue affects Greenshift Query and Meta Addon: from n/a before 3.9.2.
